Hello!

=C2=A0

It=E2=80=99s been over 2 weeks since Claude Sonnet 4.5 has launched, and we=
 hope you=E2=80=99ve been enjoying the model in Windsurf!

=C2=A0

During this time, we=E2=80=99ve been offering Sonnet 4.5 and Sonnet 4.5 (Th=
inking) at the promotional pricing of 1x and 1.5x prompt credits for Pro an=
d Teams users.

Starting at **Thursday 12:00 AM PT,** **we will be extending our promotiona=
l period for Free, Pro, and Teams users** and moving all Sonnet models to a=
 more consistent pricing structure:

=C2=A0


- **2x prompt credits for Sonnet 4.5, Sonnet 4, Sonnet 3.7, Sonnet 3.5**=20
- **3x prompt credits for Sonnet 4.5 (Thinking), Sonnet 4 (Thinking), Sonne=
t 3.7 (Thinking)**=20
This means that during this extended promotional period, you will continue =
having access to *the best deal for Sonnet 4.5 on the market.* Similar tool=
s offer Sonnet 4.5 models at the equivalent of 3x or more credits. Again, p=
lease note that this discount only applies for individual and Team users.

=C2=A0

And just as another reminder, Sonnet 3.5 will be deprecated on October 22.

=C2=A0

Best,
The Windsurf Team


900 Villa St, 94041, Mountain View

